{"tid":2305391,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蘋人誌︰像猶太人痛恨希特拉 譚得志","createTime":"2020-11-29T14:56:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-29T07:08:42.000Z","uid":25558,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcf885871211d357bf99da7f304dd0f21815200","tid":2305391,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T14:56:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201129/PJ5S5IPALFABHPXGWLWGRSKC6E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201129%2FPJ5S5IPALFABHPXGWLWGRSKC6E%2F&d=73P4J9mxZbud55ZbF8SGiX6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=8ded589b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201129%2FPJ5S5IPALFABHPXGWLWGRSKC6E%2F&h=4f711362\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201129/PJ5S5IPALFABHPXGWLWGRSKC6E/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n蘋人誌︰像猶太人痛恨希特拉 譚得志<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/PeDX51eTJ1xVj9FNaqTTJXTWgl4=/802x531/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDJCHIAQXVCQLFZSUJVLCPTC5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FPeDX51eTJ1xVj9FNaqTTJXTWgl4%3D%2F802x531%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDJCHIAQXVCQLFZSUJVLCPTC5I.jpg&h=5d9d124e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■9月17日，警方指快必涉發表煽動文字，引起憎惡藐視政府之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n人與人相遇多麼難，當初譚得志答應我們受訪，未暇見面已被捕，記者探監，落入他的窗口，終於走進他的視線，沒想過三日後收到他的信：「感謝你來拜山，你就是那位訪問陳志全離開立會，做了一版訪問那位記者嗎？感謝你關心我們，我那天說出嚟第一個搵你接受訪問，飲啤酒，是真的，酒過三巡，真話就來。」<br />\n<br />\n快必一再申請保釋被拒，離不開荔枝角收押所角落，傳說中曾蔭權住過的那間水飯房。<br />\n<br />\n有緣不散，他與前特首先後單獨囚禁於此；無緣不聚，這杯酒始終沒喝上，後會也未必有期，記者手上幾頁真話，得他同意刊出。<br />\n<br />\n縱是書信，一如親述，金句不絕，「Donald Trump不是我老竇，信拜登不如信連登。」<br />\n<br />\n讀者大抵更關心他的前路，信中寫道：「冇人估到我會有此經驗，我也不能估到我之後的情況。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：黃啟發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/scXJHrpSjATce7NKjCdwAN_JujI=/3021x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/X7ZB5NAZ6NF4HCXOGTAGT6J64I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FscXJHrpSjATce7NKjCdwAN_JujI%3D%2F3021x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FX7ZB5NAZ6NF4HCXOGTAGT6J64I.jpg&h=e99fdfa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■5月時，快必在銅鑼灣擺街站派口罩期間被警方拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uI4wDil83K-nRYca94ZCOwcLiVQ=/1739x1476/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BNA2SBM6AVGKXCNWOOLRWAU5CI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuI4wDil83K-nRYca94ZCOwcLiVQ%3D%2F1739x1476%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBNA2SBM6AVGKXCNWOOLRWAU5CI.jpg&h=1e1ba558&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■在收押所的快必曾透露連底褲也來不及添置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/f7ulxCb6Wg44Ax2GcQjwAo8EhHc=/3101x2067/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/D5Y76Q4RKVDZNOGUTNX37U4ZFE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Ff7ulxCb6Wg44Ax2GcQjwAo8EhHc%3D%2F3101x2067%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FD5Y76Q4RKVDZNOGUTNX37U4ZFE.jpg&h=1548674e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「想我收聲 我更大聲」是快必金句之一，即使被捕後仍堅持開火。<br />\n<br />\n蘋：《蘋果》記者<br />\n<br />\n譚：譚得志<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啟迪民智抗暴政<br />\n<br />\n蘋：今次控罪與街站有關，為何你明知選舉押後仍擺街站？倘若出來，是收火還是依然故我？<br />\n<br />\n譚：收火未？擺街站為乜？你一路跟開我的文字、Patreon、D100節目，你會知道我未收火，𠵱家收火，之前做的，全是白費。出到嚟第一件事做乜？飲返罐啤酒，打返次邊爐，然後，禮拜六日，街站見！我仲有大把橋，早排搞返嗰啲濕X本地旅行團，如果有心，我就開間旅行社，其實D100就係啦，個個禮拜搞「香港歷史旅行團」，台灣啲本土主義係咁㗎，唔係口旱旱一到選舉，個L個都話自己本土本土本土嗰啲本土機會主義者呀，你睇我收火未？<br />\n<br />\n擺街站為乜？............................<br />\n<br />\n蘋：我們不想用犧牲一詞，但你的付出有沒有底線？<br />\n<br />\n譚：我的付出有冇底線？我不是純粹的付出，我記得有句英文咁講：「Love what you do, do what you love.」因此，.................................<br />\n<br />\n我的底線也是我家人的底線，............................。<br />\n<br />\n所以，............................<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔收聲變眼中釘<br />\n<br />\n蘋：政府會困你多久，還有甚麼方法對付你？<br />\n<br />\n譚：真係冇得估，十年啦，我一條罪可入兩年，癲起上嚟差唔多啦，咁我律師咪上訴囉，唔通劫獄咩，特朗普同拜登會丟原子彈嗎？劉曉波都11年啦，香港有一國兩制，有保障，少一年，十年。仲有大把方法對付我，再搵啲違反人權嘅惡法告我，實搵到㗎，夾硬上庭，個官又唔畀我保釋，冇成本好易做，咁係最文明的手段了，愛國做任何事都唔犯法，梁振英講嘅，預咗唔使驚，一係就收聲。<br />\n<br />\n蘋：為何人民力量成為政府眼中釘、肉中刺？慢必本人也是打壓對象，自顧不暇？<br />\n<br />\n譚：點解人民力量成為政府眼中釘？............................<br />\n<br />\n加上我哋冇改政綱，冇摺埋個字頭，點解？............................................<br />\n<br />\n其實個暴政已經對我同人力好好，.....................<br />\n<br />\n慢必自顧不暇嗎？........................<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uTwDQH0IkBcV71JiIalwD2_m0PA=/1686x1223/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/MWX2SLB5JBG3VA4QKEGK74M4L4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuTwDQH0IkBcV71JiIalwD2_m0PA%3D%2F1686x1223%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FMWX2SLB5JBG3VA4QKEGK74M4L4.jpg&h=3df9dc95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■經快必授權義工助理整理後的回信內容，仍能感受到他那團火。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NRxKM405-Z7UYpJOWwO4EXrkzPw=/1868x1772/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ILNLWW6RZBCRXOQAM6OX55XJAA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNRxKM405-Z7UYpJOWwO4EXrkzPw%3D%2F1868x1772%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FILNLWW6RZBCRXOQAM6OX55XJAA.jpg&h=7a22b1e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■擺街站在快必口中，就如播道傳福音一樣啟迪民智。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n要有博拉的準備<br />\n<br />\n蘋：社會運動由開始到沉寂，有何總結？<br />\n<br />\n譚：點總結呀？咁多人死咗，咁多應該死全家嘅未死，咁多人冇咗隻眼，點總結啫？繼續用各種方法，到死誓相隨囉，要有一種「猶太人痛恨納粹希特拉」的級數去痛恨暴政，要有一種「228死難家屬」的哀痛，去找這個暴政算賬，我唔會講嗰啲「每場運動都有起有跌」，「冷咗落嚟嘅其實係蓄勢待發」呢啲說話，應用各種方法報仇，而不是自欺欺人。<br />\n<br />\n我總覺得，我們未ready，未夠，...............................<br />\n<br />\n蘋：泛民今後還有何玩法？<br />\n<br />\n譚：如果冇選舉，就要博拉，博拉，再博拉，G phone、肥佬黎、周庭，拉之餘要入獄，要坐監，引發世界反應，如果你話：........................<br />\n<br />\n我講咗幾年啦，當年民主派有高山大會，..........................<br />\n<br />\n哈維爾出過很多書，..................."},{"pid":"043090f96f5ad26f34ee2ca141f03b9f4dc4d47c","tid":2305391,"uid":96486,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T15:01:53.000Z","msg":"咁多位抗爭人士，呢個我都佩服呢個<br />\n係咁嚴厲既國安法下，敢於表達政見"},{"pid":"3f05c4c329bcdf570d1de638ff3dd21fd5255f47","tid":2305391,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T05:00:29.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"91d2694061b089a0382cd32af8e90eadaf97569e","tid":2305391,"uid":55379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:06:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mousexm/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeceda93e624056dcc5419f698a72c4f215a494f","tid":2305391,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:11:43.000Z","msg":"推，如果連呢個尺度都接受唔到<br />\n香港真係不適宜居住，指標黎"},{"pid":"49e9c4b5b177729d28079a4775a8712151d342e7","tid":2305391,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:11:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2fbf4b2ae6c3c7ef70aef724cc31c5e50cf9f9","tid":2305391,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"31cf0c8e74c3dc954c4c3be96bab9ac109d0e0f7","tid":2305391,"uid":100930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4c63b17c9a23bc69ffe6ed168cda88f3e44b0a2","tid":2305391,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T07:08:42.000Z","msg":"請珍惜快必...（認真）"}]}